  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You've spent a lifetime fighting, with the scars to prove it. You gain the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Increase your Constitution score by 1, to a maximum of 20.</li>\n<li>When you roll a 19 or a 20 on the [[/r d20]] for a death saving throw, you regain 1 hit point. </li>\n<li>When you are reduced to 0 hit points but not killed outright, you can drop to 1 hit point instead. Once you've used this ability, you must complete a long rest before you can use it again.</li></ul>",
